      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, budget-friendly option for daily transportation. The exterior shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings on the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some staining consistent with regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and handles well, though it may benefit from a routine tune-up in the near future. It is a practical choice for someone prioritizing functionality and value over a perfect aesthetic.",
