      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this car to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, so there\u2019s not a scratch on it and the interior is spotless. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
