    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1993 Mazda RX-7 featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine. This example maintains factory-spec sequential twin-turbochargers, delivering seamless boost across the powerband via a meticulously inspected vacuum system. The chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining its original double-wishbone aluminum suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential for unparalleled kinematic feedback. Every fluid has been sampled and replaced, ensuring the apex seals operate within optimal thermal parameters. Finished in pristine factory paint with a zero-wear interior, this FD represents the pinnacle of 50/50 weight distribution and analog performance. Compression test results are superlative across all rotor faces.",
      "price": 44500.0,
