      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a definitive example of its kind. This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine with a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections of any kind. The wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any bolster wear, and the interior still retains its original factory scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This sale includes the full set of original keys, the complete owner's manual portfolio, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key, collector-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the dealership floor.",
